data.description: This recently refurbished ranch-style home features four bedrooms and two bathrooms. The living room stands out with its lovely cathedral ceilings, complemented by a fresh coat of paint and enhanced by brand-new carpeting throughout. The main living areas and bathrooms now have modern laminate flooring. Additionally, the property offers a generous 0.6-acre fenced backyard. The kitchen refrigerator and outdoor storage shed remain with the home. This residence is a definite must-see!  Old Republic Home Warranty now included with accepted offer.
